data.description: Step into the epitome of modern living at 10744 S Oquie Rd, South Jordan! This home boasts an array of sought-after features, including energy-efficient upgrades designed to elevate your lifestyle.The kitchen dazzles with its quartz countertop, with A island equipped with extra storage . Walk in pantry as well a extra pantry .  Offering both style and functional space . Picture yourself savoring the view of the temple while creating culinary masterpieces in this inviting space.  The master bedroom isn't just a room; it's a sanctuary, offering an amazing walk in closet and a luxurious attached bath. With a tankless water heater, this home ensures a constant supply of hot water, catering to your comfort.  Moreover, this home boasts a brand-new carpet with double padding for that extra touch of comfort. Not to mention, It's custom Paint . It's equipped with an Energy Star furnace, maximizing efficiency and minimizing energy costs while keeping you cozy during colder seasons.  If that wasn't enough, its prime location places you just a 15-minute stroll from the new Bees ballpark, perfect for sports enthusiasts or those seeking entertainment close to home.  Come experience the harmonious blend of contemporary amenities, stunning views, and energy-efficient living at 10744 S Oquie Rd.
